275
00:12:43,730 --> 00:12:45,498
I just liked the feeling

276
00:12:45,565 --> 00:12:48,167
that one person thinks
I'm good at something.

277
00:12:48,234 --> 00:12:50,136
I get it, Homie.

278
00:12:50,203 --> 00:12:52,505
But if you really want
to help this guy,

279
00:12:52,572 --> 00:12:54,440
help him grow up.

280
00:12:57,910 --> 00:12:59,512
Come on, Fordham,

281
