do you have any other dreams?

288
00:13:17,930 --> 00:13:20,566
Ah, man, you are
mentoring me hard right now.

289
00:13:20,633 --> 00:13:23,236
Oh, okay, I'm gonna tell you,
but don't laugh.

290
00:13:23,303 --> 00:13:24,671
I won't.

291
00:13:24,737 --> 00:13:26,306
Slices.

292
00:13:26,372 --> 00:13:28,641
Nothing better than getting
a slice of pizza, right?

293
00:13:28,708 --> 00:13:31,678
