the heat lamp all dried out.

294
00:13:31,744 --> 00:13:33,579
Damn heat lamp.

295
00:13:33,646 --> 00:13:36,416
Right. So why not make the pizza
one slice at a time,

296
00:13:36,482 --> 00:13:37,583
