297
00:13:37,650 --> 00:13:39,686
Every slice is Derek Jeter.

298
00:13:39,752 --> 00:13:41,854
No Scott Brosius in the bunch.

299
00:13:41,921 --> 00:13:43,890
That's genius!

300
00:13:43,956 --> 00:13:46,092
Oh, my God,
I can't believe you like it.

301
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:49,362
Mike! You know what you
should call your slices?

302
00:13:49,429 --> 00:13:51,597
Mike's Slices.

303
00:13:51,664 --> 00:13:53,099
