309
00:14:05,078 --> 00:14:07,113
Every slice a Jeter.

310
00:14:07,180 --> 00:14:09,916
No Scott Brosiuses.

311
00:14:09,982 --> 00:14:12,919
Why can't I get a whole pizza
and slice it myself?

312
00:14:12,985 --> 00:14:14,454
There are no whole pizzas.

313
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:17,056
It's just slices, hot and fresh.

314
00:14:17,123 --> 00:14:19,892
And don't worry about investing
with this guy, Mr. Burns,

315
00:14:19,959 --> 00:14:22,395
because he's backed
by the full mentorship

316
00:14:22,462 --> 00:14:24,764
of Homer J. Simpsons.

317
00:14:24,831 --> 00:14:27,266
Then it's my pleasure
to tell you...

318
00:14:27,333 --> 00:14:30,903
