hep-C Dracula!

334
00:15:11,711 --> 00:15:13,179
By the way,
he's off his happy pills.

335
00:15:17,817 --> 00:15:20,186
You're lucky Mr. Burns's gun
was 200 years old.

336
00:15:20,253 --> 00:15:21,754
Yeah, but now my doctor says

337
00:15:21,821 --> 00:15:23,823
I can't get shot
in the face again.

338
00:15:23,890 --> 00:15:25,825
Who's ugly now, pellet-head?

339
00:15:28,895 --> 00:15:30,830
Come on, it's okay. Don't cry.

340
00:15:30,897 --> 00:15:33,800
I'm not. All the BBs in my head
are making it heavy.

341
00:15:33,866 --> 00:15:35,501
Mike, this is all my fault.

342
00:15:35,568 --> 00:15:38,371
I know you think I'm a great
nuclear guy, but I'm not.

343
00:15:38,438 --> 00:15:40,273
I didn't stop those accidents.

344
00:15:40,339 --> 00:15:41,808
I caused them.

345
00:15:41,874 --> 00:15:43,543
Huh? No. No.

346
00:15:43,609 --> 00:15:45,478
All my posters...
Bet on Yourself.

347
00:15:45,545 --> 00:15:47,213
Go Big or Go Home.

348
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:50,016
