from a poster store.

349
00:15:50,082 --> 00:15:53,586
I was trying to go big, and
they wouldn't let me go home.

350
00:15:53,653 --> 00:15:57,190
Mike, face it, I'm a bad mentor.

351
00:15:57,256 --> 00:15:59,725
No one disrespects
Homer Simpsons.

352
00:15:59,792 --> 00:16:01,360
Not even you.

353
00:16:01,427 --> 00:16:03,863
You're the best mentor
a lousy bride-banger like me

354
00:16:03,930 --> 00:16:05,264
could ever ask for.

355
00:16:05,331 --> 00:16:07,133
And I'm gonna prove it.

356
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:08,701
Who spilled BBs

357
00:16:08,768 --> 00:16:10,937
all over the...

358
00:16:12,939 --> 00:16:16,142
Yo! Mentor!

359
00:16:21,147 --> 00:16:23,382
Anybody want a slice of pizza

360
00:16:23,449 --> 00:16:25,551
