361
00:16:25,618 --> 00:16:27,587
Where'd you get a food truck?

362
00:16:27,653 --> 00:16:30,523
It's all cause of you, mentor,
all cause of you. Deal with it.

363
00:16:30,590 --> 00:16:32,758
The boys and I
will take a large pie.

364
00:16:32,825 --> 00:16:34,861
Can't you read a truck,
Cookie Puss?

365
00:16:34,927 --> 00:16:36,095
Slices only!

366
00:16:36,162 --> 00:16:38,030
All righty,
three slices, please.

367
00:16:38,097 --> 00:16:41,734
They'll be ready in 13,
26 and 39 minutes.

368
00:16:41,801 --> 00:16:43,903
And don't block the window,
sizzle chest.

369
00:16:43,970 --> 00:16:46,572
When will my slice be ready?

370
00:16:46,639 --> 00:16:49,275
And by slice,
I mean the first payment

371
00:16:49,342 --> 00:16:51,777
on your outstanding loan.

372
00:16:51,844 --> 00:16:54,580
You borrowed money
from the mob?!

373
00:16:54,647 --> 00:16:56,549
No, no, no, no, no, no.
It's all good.

374
00:16:56,616 --> 00:16:59,752
I took a one-week loan from
Fat Tony for a hundred grand.

375
00:16:59,819 --> 00:17:01,687
I put $50k into the truck

376
00:17:01,754 --> 00:17:04,190
and then bet the other 50
on tonight's Lehigh game,

377
00:17:04,257 --> 00:17:05,658
which is a lock.

378
00:17:05,725 --> 00:17:08,060
