401
00:18:02,381 --> 00:18:03,883
Guns up.

402
00:18:03,950 --> 00:18:05,918
Safeties off.

403
00:18:09,055 --> 00:18:10,389
Don't worry, I know a place

404
00:18:10,456 --> 00:18:11,891
where they will never find us.

405
00:18:15,061 --> 00:18:19,131
A food truck graveyard.

406
00:18:25,071 --> 00:18:27,640
Why are there
so many failed ones?

407
00:18:27,707 --> 00:18:30,710
'Cause they don't have
an original concept, like me.

408
00:18:48,461 --> 00:18:50,062
Homer, I got to tell you
one thing.

409
00:18:50,129 --> 00:18:51,530
Your boy's not ugly.

410
00:18:51,597 --> 00:18:52,865
He's gorgeous.

411
00:18:52,932 --> 00:18:54,400
Just like his old man.

412
00:18:54,467 --> 00:18:55,901
