slice of triangular dough.

417
00:19:08,748 --> 00:19:12,785
Before the end,
we will share a pie.

418
00:19:12,852 --> 00:19:15,087
It's just slices,
you goombah caveman!

419
00:19:16,288 --> 00:19:18,524
Usually a slice
is dried out

420
00:19:18,591 --> 00:19:21,560
